creator: Jetcost
descriptionHtml:
Hotels, apartments, B&Bs, hostels and much more! Find your ideal stay with hotelscan and save money by comparing offers from nearly 3,000,000 accommodations and more than 100 worldwide booking sites.

Your easiest hotel search starts now! Here are 5 reasons that will make you love hotelscan’s app:

1. Compare prices of hotels, apartments, holiday homes and more from the best booking sites like Booking.com, Expedia, Airbnb, Agoda and many others;
2. Discover the most suitable offer for your needs thanks to reviews, photo gallery, amenities and so on;
3. See your latest searches and don't miss the offers that caught your eye;
4. Bookmark your favourite hotels & accommodation to check availability at any time.

Download hotelscan to discover new hotels & accommodation at the best price. hotelscan’s app is totally free, and you won't be charged any extra costs on the price of your booking.

Easily compare hotel offers with hotelscan features: view the accommodation you are interested in on the map and browse nearby offers. You will find the best place for your stay, always according to your choices.

Don’t waste time and money. With hotelscan you’ll have everything you need to plan your next trip stress-free. Find the best hotels, B&Bs, apartments, hostels, holiday homes, camps, motels and much more.

Take advantage of exceptional deals, thanks to hotelscan’s partners. Take a look in advance at what your stay will look like with high-quality pictures of hotels and rooms. The reviews of other travellers will also help you discover points of strength and weakness of all accommodations.

Make your search unique: search hotels & accommodation by city, neighbourhood, attraction or hotel name with just one tap. Filters will let you choose a price range, the minimum rating score, hotel stars, type of accommodation and amenities like Wi-Fi, pool and fitness area;

If you’re looking for a Hotel search app, hotelscan is definitely your first choice. Download it now!
descriptionShort: Find only the best accommodation and save on your next trip with hotelscan!
